

## main part
- read txt, csv / multiple files in a folder
- detect data type
- sava data into mysql database

## features of the program

# after defined time reindex/import new data -- specific data type search(?)
- new data with last modified in ascending order
- after data import move the file to archive folder -- in archive format which can be user defined

# messages of the program stored in a file
- display those messages onscreen
- the message needs to entail timestamp

# configutation file which is read by start of the program
- file type from import file
- file type for archive file
- file type for error type
- time between reindex/search of new files (in seconds)
- database connection configuration

## error check

# while starting the programm
- check for configuration file
- if missing or wrong value terminate program with message to user

# during work in program 
- check if found files can be opened and read
- check for syntax id 661, 662, 664, 669
- all fields with id needs to contain value
- check for character correct in numeric field
- check for correct date and time in transfer date and time
- the 664 id amount should match the number in 669
- if error while reading file, move it into error foleder and log it

## mysql table 

table 1:
MESSAGEID eindeutige NachrichtenID
FILENAME Dateiname der eingelesenen Datei
ORDERNO Bestellnummer
TRANSMISSION Übertragungsdatum und –zeit
SUPPLIER Lieferantennummer
CUSTOMER Kundennummer
REFERENCENO Kennnummer des Bauteils
COMMODITY Teileartgruppe des Bauteils

table 2:
MESSAGEID eindeutige NachrichtenID
POSITION fortlaufende Positionsnummer zur NachrichtenID (ab 1)
ITEMNO Artikelnummer
QUANTITY bestellte Menge
ITEMTYPE Teileart 

# primary and foreign key MESSAGEID -- 1:n-Relation 
- per file MESSAGEID primary key auto_increment 
